Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New Zealand bans US navy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xjfn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Feb 1985
New Zealand's new premier brings in promised nuclear ban - resulting in a US navy destroyer being turned away from port of call. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less